<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>222</hymn_number>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw a tlau i a bami ra kir tuah, Tuukhal tha nih cun an lem lengmang
 ko, Khamh awkah an kawl, thianh awkah an hngah, Rau lo te-in a sinah ra
 kir tuah.

[C1]
   Nem tein an auh, Thinfual in an nawl, Tuukhal tha an auh-nak kha
   ngai tuah, Nem te-in an auh, thinfual in an nawl, Dawtnak in, &quot;Ka sin ra
   tuah,&quot; an ti.

[V2]
 An hngah ko rih zeica-ah na thih lai? Saupi tuu run chungin tlau cang
 hmanhlaw, A nunnak thi in nangmah kha an tlanh, Khuaruahhar dawtnak chim
 khawh lomi cu.

[C2]
   Nem tein an auh, Thinfual in an nawl, Tuukhal tha an auh-nak kha
   ngai tuah, Nem te-in an auh, thinfual in an nawl, Dawtnak in, &quot;Ka sin ra
   tuah,&quot; an ti.

[V3]
 A bia kha ngai tuah, a dawtnak ruat tuah, Nangmah sualnak kha thing
 cungah a in, Ngaihthiamnak tling le zungzal nunnak cu, A sermi remnak
 thawngin an pek cang.

[C3]
   Nem tein an auh, Thinfual in an nawl, Tuukhal tha an auh-nak kha
   ngai tuah, Nem te-in an auh, thinfual in an nawl, Dawtnak in, &quot;Ka sin ra
   tuah,&quot; an ti.

[V4]
 Lam ding in lut tuah, Lamtak in lut tuah, Jesuh in lut tuah, inn-ka
 kha a si, Amah nih nem te-in an auh lengmang, Ra lut tuah law tlau than
 ti lo dingin.

[C4]
   Nem tein an auh, Thinfual in an nawl, Tuukhal tha an auh-nak kha
   ngai tuah, Nem te-in an auh, thinfual in an nawl, Dawtnak in, &quot;Ka sin ra
   tuah,&quot; an ti.</lyrics>
<title>NEM TEIN AN AUH CH222</title>
</song>